      "text": [
        "وَقَوْلُهُ: «وَ هامَتْ دَوابُّنا» اَىْ عَطِشَتْ، وَالْهُيامُ: الْعَطْشُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "His words “wa hamat dawābbuna” means became thirsty, as “huyam” means thirst."
        ]
      }
